reviews.review_text: The restaurant definitely feels like a blast from the past, it kinda smells like commercial so cigarettes and weed which is not my favourite and its kinda drafty but it adds to the experience and me and my friends are kinda crazy so 5 stars. The food is also decent, they have a big variety and its pretty good. Overall I think its a fun experience to come with friends. I really like their deep fried prawns. And I want to try their brunch here too. The photos are from 2 separate times we went.
Amazing place for a quick and tasteful breakfast/brunch! Would come back again Food : 5/5
This is a very peaceful restaurant with a delicious menu for a very reasonable price! Portions are big
We love coming here. Just had the B2 combo. So satisfying. The ladies are so awewome.
Affordable prices, but cash only. Very large portions, so visit with an appetite.
I dont know how to order anything but this BBQ pork noodle soup Super generous with the pork, I mean, you can hardly see the noodles! Bok choy also hidden under there!

My SO and I came here for brunch and the food portions were big and decently priced. May not be the prettiest looking establishment but thats what I find to be so great about this place. With good food like this, I definitely recommend people to try this place out. I love all day breakfast and chinese food so this place checks both boxes. Service was prompt and servers were attentive. Note this place is CASH ONLY though.
Large portions for the combo plates at a fair price. I frequently come here and the server remembers my order and is kind. Remember to bring cash as it is cash only.

Im always a satisfied customer sharing a booth with family, friends or the newspaper! Efficient yet friendly staff serve up delicious meals for breakfast, lunch and dinner.  The food is always good whether the ubiquitous BLT sandwich or my favorite chicken & green bean in black bean sauce. You cant go wrong with the fresh food and reasonable prices...
Ive been coming here for years, and I have never had any bad experiences. Food is always done well. They take large groups and family events. Definitely would recommend it. Food
Always great food. Always great service the lady knows our order.
Older place but the food is awesome and service is very good and I definitely will go there again
It s so nice meals , Thank You

I ened up eating here at least 1 or 2 times a week. The service is friendly and very homey ( it feels like going to my friends house for dinner) always greeted with a smile and how are you. Whether its their house burger or their Chinese food combo, you will never be disappointed with the food you get from Kyles kitchen

One of the best Food here for a good price. Ive been going here for over 10 years plus really good a must try. My favourites are the broccoli & chicken with black bean sauce on steamed or either green beans with beef either or. The burgers and French fries taste really good to.
Great breakfast special till 11am, I also love their veggie omelette. Friendly staff and food is always HOT! Cash only, greasy spoon diner, One of the last standing gems in Vancouver
This is my favorite place to eat out at, The waiter Even remembers my usual Poutine and Chicken balls haha To bad I cant come here Too often And again overall Great place
good food reasonable.prices,I like their dinner special the most always Chinese dish heaping serving for only 10$
As I sat to eat I got to witness a assault on another customer by thugs who thought it appropriate to pull bear spray out in a restaurant

Great diner fare! We make a point of coming to Kyles Cafe each time we are in Vancouver for their burgers. Classic Canadian diner style burgers - homemade patties, good toppings. Plenty of fries and gravy on the side. The Beef dip is also very good. We are always happy with the food, service, and prices. This is not a fancy place, just a good Chinese-Canadian diner with good food at reasonable prices. Love it.
The staff there is so wonderful. The good is reasonable priced. They serve to anyone. I eat there all the time. Their hours are fantastic. Very delicious menu. They even serve breakfast.
Excellent food at local restaurant on Commercial Drive. Been going since 2007. Recommend this restaurant to anyone.
2 Budweiser    she always knew what we wanted to drink! Even at 10:50am on a Sunday morning   AMAZING FOOD and soooooo affordable
Nice atmosphere...very neighborly... On another note, the washrooms need a thorough cleaning...PLEASE!!!! Food
After two years of COVID, most of Vancouver has gotten worse but Kyle s has only gotten better.
First time visit with friends. A simple mom and pop type restaurant. Had a veggie omelet with home fries and toast. Under $10.  Simple, fresh, deelish....Great variety...highly recommend this one.
Every neighbourhood needs a small local cafe to call your own.  This is mine. Friendly staff. Excellent service. Best prices. Best deal near here for breakfast.
This awesome lil Cafe has been our go to for years great food, awesome prices and friendly staff...have never had a bad meal or service.

$12.xx special Chowmein is great for a hearty appetite or split for lunch next day. Waitress Sammy is always so gracious. P.S. there is One washroom only and they are located across the street from Commercial-Broadway Skytrain Station.
One of my favorite places to eat. Great food and staff. Nice friendly environment.  Love that staff kno alot of the people who go their
Awesome food , nice friendly staff. Children friendly. Clean washrooms.  Daily specials. Decent prices.
Great value, huge portions. Yum.

Zero artifice. Reasonable prices and a million menu options. It isnt trendy or hip, but it is dependable and good. Consider it if you want a meal because you just want food, and let the real you hang out for a bit, free of judgement.
Food was excellent as always service is always impeccable Order to serve time is super quick Definitely one of Vancitys Landmark restaurants.
Love this place variety of Canadian or Chinese food. Great staff.
No nonsense Canadian-Chinese greasy spoon. Good vegetarian cuisine too! I m glad to have Kyles close by, and within a decent price range.

Its like having a piece of country in the city. My family has been going here for years. It was one of the first places my Moms took me when I moved to the city from Bella Coola.
It was delicious! Service is so so.
Classic Vancouver breakfast joint. Quick service, very cheap western style breakfast options. Decent coffee.Havent tried their chinese but ive heard its good. Cash only.

Awesome Staff and the assortment of meals an deals with covid safety measures in place, makes this the place to be!!  Stay safe everyone!!
